{"word":"H1554 - גַּלִּים - Gallîym - gal-leem' - Gallim","slug":"H1554","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גַּלִּים</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Gallîym"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gal-leem'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gallim"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>גּלּים</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>gallı̂ym</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>gal-leem'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Gallim = \"springs\" <ol><li>a place north of Jerusalem, home town of the man to whom Michal, Saul's daughter, David's wife, was given as wife by Saul even though she was already married to David</li></ol> <p />Origin: plural of <a href=\"#/H1530\">H1530</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1019\">H1019</a>, <a href=\"#/H1530\">H1530</a>, <a href=\"#/H1531\">H1531</a>, <a href=\"#/H1534\">H1534</a>, <a href=\"#/H1536\">H1536</a>, <a href=\"#/H1537\">H1537</a>, <a href=\"#/H1538\">H1538</a>, <a href=\"#/H1543\">H1543</a>, <a href=\"#/H1544\">H1544</a>, <a href=\"#/H1550\">H1550</a>, <a href=\"#/H1551\">H1551</a>, <a href=\"#/H1552\">H1552</a>, <a href=\"#/H1553\">H1553</a>, <a href=\"#/H1556\">H1556</a>, <a href=\"#/H1557\">H1557</a>, <a href=\"#/H1559\">H1559</a>, <a href=\"#/H1561\">H1561</a>, <a href=\"#/H1562\">H1562</a>, <a href=\"#/H1567\">H1567</a>, <a href=\"#/H4039\">H4039</a>"}]}